[Would someone with epidemiological experience of Hepatitis A infections
please explain how one can have high attack rates in two Michigan schools
but nothing elsewhere - all presumeably sharing the same distribution of
these frozen strawberries processed in April & May, 1996. MHJ
.............................................mhj
